\id 2TH 2TƐ - Bible Iyansi
\h 2 TƐSALƆNIKÀ
\toc1 Un'kaan wàyweel akà Bàtɛsalɔnikà
\toc2 2 TƐSALƆNIKÀ
\toc3 2Tɛ
\mt2 Un'kaan wàyweel akà
\mt1 Bàtɛsalɔnikà
\imt1 Nsɛmà
\ip Un'kaan a Pɔl wàyweel akà Bàtɛsalɔnikà afuurà ndaa bàtɛn uboo a un'kaan wàtàtwɛb: ngyeel a Mwol unsà làkoo. Ntɔn bàmbɔɔn bàfàkyey uyɔl naa ngyeel ayi yàkyàkwo itaan, un'kaan awà akwen mudwa an'kyän an'be amà.
\is1 Kiin a ndaa
\ip Asànaa unsà un'kaan wàtàtwɛb, Pɔl, Silàvɛ anà Tumàtɛ ban'pà mbɔr akà baar ban'söön ba un'kaan 1.1-2.
\ip Wa wàŋakab mbwo yweel: Mbwo yàtàtwɛb yàŋàyaamà unsà ngyööb. Yà nsɛmà, nde asɔnà iköŋ a ngwal, itàkal naa mpay a nkwaaŋ: nde an'tüüb anà an'lɔŋ unsà ntsuul a ndaa a Nzam taaŋ usàmɛnà Mwol Yɛsu. Ikal kyàyweel ikanà làkwikilà a aklistɔ ntɔn muyöb balàbal a « ilä a Mwol » anà muyilɔn. Mbwo yàyweel yà ndaa mupà ngwal. Mbwo yà ntsüü yà ntɔn mbɔr a Pɔl anà musà kɔɔ. Un'kaan wàyweel wà akà Bàtɛsalɔnikà ntsüü awa, yà balàbal asànaa un'kaan wàtàtwɛb. Nde wa kàsön ntsü a mbul 51 itàkal 52 utaaŋ abi là. Wa kàläb mbwo nsil ya ayà kun'kaan wàtàtwɛb. Mbeel ayi yà ntɔn bi iduub mii anà iyamà Nzam awà Taaràbi: « Itsuuŋ bi unsube » (Màtay 6.13).
\c 1
\s1 Mbɔr
\p 
\v 1 Pɔl, Silàvɛ anà Tumutɛ.
\p Bi ban'pà mbɔr akà Ikööŋ akyà kyà Taa Nzam anà kyà Mwol Yɛsu Klistɔ:
\v 2 Wɛy Taaràbi Nzam anà Mwol Yɛsu Klistɔ bàlapɛ kab a ngway anà duu!
\s1 Nsaŋ mpal usàyà Yɛsu
\p 
\v 3 Atɔŋ, taaŋ lanswà bi ikyer afuur an'tɔɔn akà Nzam ntɔn bɛ. Yubwaŋ naa bi ikyer abun, ntɔn làkwikilà abɛ làmuyɛl mbɔɔn, anà ukwen a umwɛy umwɛy uboo a bɛ akatɔŋ bumwɛy bàsöönà.
\v 4 Kyakin ifàswaŋ bi ngaal uboo a Ikööŋ a Nzam ntɔn muküünà abɛ anà làkwikilà abɛ unsà nkwaaŋ anà mpay aŋàdiir làmanà bɛ.
\p 
\v 5 Abà ya ikamɛɛyà ntsüül a nsaŋ a Nzam yàbalàbal, ntɔn bɛ làmɛnà bàŋàkwo ntɔn Imwol a Nzam akyà làmanà bɛ mpay.
\v 6 Ya yà balàbal naa Nzam ufuur ngyɛb aŋàdiir akà baar bàfàlapà unkiiŋ,
\v 7 anà nde afàpà, akà bɛ baar làmanà mpay, ngyɔ̈ɔ̈r anà akà bi, umpal a imɛɛy a Mwol Yɛsu fà du anà akyeey ande bunkaak a ngwal.
\v 8 Nde asàyà uboo a làlem a mbaa ntɔn mupà ntaaŋàmbar akà baar mpa bàyöb Nzam anà mpa bàfàkyey Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ a Mwol abi Yɛsu.
\v 9 Ntaaŋàmbar aba isàkal bwà a mbul a in'tye, ukwɛl kusà a Mwol anà làkoo ande làngwal,
\v 10 mpal usàyà nde muwal làkoo amu aŋin'kyɛɛl ande anà itääŋ amu aŋàlàkwikilà, kyekà bɛ làkyey imbäl abi.
\v 11 Kyakin bi ikayamà taaŋ lanswà ntɔn bɛ, ntɔn Nzam abi kàlabuul bàŋàkwo mukal uboo a mbeel kàlasi nde, anà, u mbwo a ngwal ande, nde kàlabay mukwey ngyal abɛ mukyer ubwaŋ anà làkwikilà làfàmɛnà unsà isal.
\v 12 Abun, bɛ làsàsyaŋà ikɔb a Mwol abi Yɛsu anà nde sye akyer asàlasyaŋà, asànaa làkwen kab a ngway a Nzam abi anà là Mwol Yɛsu Klistɔ.
\c 2
\s1 Umbarà a ntsüü
\p 
\v 1 Atɔŋ, ntɔn ndaa iler ngyeel a Mwol abi Yɛsu Klistɔ anà nköŋ abi apà nde, bi kàmàlalɔɔm:
\v 2 isàkal naa imɛɛy mwɛy kyàngɔɔm, itàkal ndaa a mbuur mwɛy, itàkal ndaa a un'kaan mwɛy bàmɛɛy naa yàfü akà bi, yàmàlakyään naa ilä a Mwol kyà kyàyà itaan, twon lan'düül musà lingyoomà unsà an'kyän abɛ itàkal muman bɔɔmà ntɔn ya.
\v 3 Wɛy akà mbuur mwɛy ukɔ̈ɔ̈n akàlabwiy ndwaŋ, itàkal kaben. Ntɔn kusà a ilä aki muyà, baar mbɔɔn bàtwab atàpiy làkwikilà anà aŋufur a nkyɛl awà un'kyàbwà, utwab atàmɛnà,
\v 4 nde mbuur afàmbarà anà afàmbäär undiir wanswà bàfàbel naa nzam itàkal naa undiir wanswà bàfàsà làkoo. Nde afàkàbwaay tii u ndwà a Nzam anà mukyään nde ŋakwo naa nde wà Nzam.
\v 5 Nkye bɛ làfàkayɔbà anki naa mɛ kàkyàlakyään ndaa ayin utaaŋ kàkäl mɛ tsütsü apà bɛ?
\v 6 Apanà, bɛ làkyàyöb undiir akun'taa mpi ntɔn nde uyàmɛnà nà utaaŋ kàyöŋà Nzam ntɔn nde.
\v 7 Ntɔn ngyee a ube yàkyàsɛmà musal. Yan'sal nà mulwom mbuur akataa wa mpi,
\v 8 apan mbuur un'be waa usàmɛnà, mbuur usàdwa Mwol Yɛsu u mbwo a un'swey a mun ande, anà asun'buul undiir a bunàbun u mbwo a in'nyääŋ a ngyeel ande.
\v 9 Mbuur un'be asàyà u ngwal a Satanà, nde asàkyer isal a ngwal byifà ifà, impà, idiim a loor,
\v 10 anà mbwo yanswà mpa ayà balàbal ntɔn mukur baar bàdiimà mbwo, ntɔn ba bàwɛl anki ukwen a ndandaa abà bàlawiiy mɔ̈ɔ̈.
\v 11 Kyakin Nzam katöömà nde ngwal a ndiimà ntɔn ba bàsi làkwikilà u ndaa a loor,
\v 12 ntɔn baar banswà mpa bàsi làkwikilà amu ndandaa, wɛɛ bàmɛn un'sak ntɔn ndaa mpa ayà balàbal, bàwɛl ntaaŋàmbar.
\s1 Bɛ bàlasɔ̈ɔ̈l ntɔn muwà mɔ̈ɔ̈
\p 
\v 13 Atɔŋ, akà bi, bi ikyer afuur an'tɔɔn akà Nzam taaŋ lanswà ntɔn bɛ, nkween a Mwol, ntɔn Nzam kàlasɔ̈ɔ̈l fà nsɛmà, ntɔn bɛ làwü mɔ̈ɔ̈ u mbwo a Dweelà afàkyɛɛl anà u mbwo a làkwikilà amu ndandaa.
\v 14 Ntɔn ya sye, nde kàlabel u mbwo a Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ kàlakyään bi, ntɔn bɛ làwɛl kab unsà làkoo a Mwol abi Yɛsu Klistɔ.
\v 15 Kyakin, atɔŋ, làkäl aŋàtsim anà làkäär an'lɔɔŋ kàlapɛ bi, itàkal u mun, itàkal unsun'kaan.
\p 
\v 16 Wɛy Mwol abi Yɛsu Klistɔ nde ŋakwo, anà Taaràbi Nzam, awà kikwen, anà u mbwo a kab a ngway ande, kipɛ ndɛɛl a mbul a in'tye anà làkyän aŋàbwaŋ,
\v 17 bàlalɛɛl anà bàlapɛ ngwal amu isal kyanswà anà ndaa aŋàbwaŋ yanswà.
\c 3
\s1 Làyamà ntɔn bi
\p 
\v 1 Abun, atɔŋ, làyamà ntɔn bi, ntɔn ndaa a Mwol ipää agyägyä, anà ya iwɛl làkoo asànaa iwà ya akà bɛ,
\v 2 ntɔn bi isɔrà akaŋankyɛl anà akà baar abe, ntɔn ba banswà làkwikilà latɛy.
\v 3 Wɛɛ Mwol wà lää: nde ayàlapà ngwal anà ayàlatii ukwɛl a Mbuur un'be.
\v 4 Bi ifàsà mpem akà Mwol ntɔn bɛ, ntɔn bɛ làfàkyer indiir ifàlaswaŋ bi, anà bɛ làsàlalà mukyer bya.
\p 
\v 5 Wɛy Mwol ulɔ̈ɔ̈n mpem abɛ ntɔn mukwen Nzam anà unsà nkääŋ a mpem a Klistɔ!
\s1 Ndöŋ a isal
\p 
\v 6 Atɔŋ, bi bàmàlaswaŋ kà ikɔb a Mwol Yɛsu Klistɔ: làkäl ukwɛl a un'tɔŋ awe anà mɔ̈ɔ̈ a ŋingyäy anà mpa afàlab an'lɔɔŋ làwɛl bɛ akà bi.
\v 7 Bɛ, bɛ ŋakwo làkyàyöb ubwaŋ naa bɛ bi lilab aben: bi kàkäl anki anà mɔ̈ɔ̈ a ŋingyäy uboo a bɛ.
\v 8 Bi kàdi anki mampà a mbuur màngway, wɛɛ, unsà mpay anà ngyɔ̈ɔ̈n, u mpib anà u mwäänà, bi kàsäl ntɔn mukɔɔn akal buur akà umwɛy uboo a bɛ.
\v 9 Iswaŋà anki naa bi kàkäl anki anà ikɔ̈b muwal mbaay abɛ, wɛɛ bi kàkwen mukal mban lan'kwo bɛ mulab.
\v 10 Kyakin, mpal kàkäl bi akà bɛ, bi kàlapɛ nswɛɛŋ yi: « Mbuur mpa akwen musal, wɛy nde ukɔɔn adyà sye! »
\p 
\v 11 Kyekà, bi iweemà naa uboo a bɛ bye anà abwal, isal aba nà uyibilà u ndaa a baar asin.
\v 12 Akà abwal aban, bi kan'pà nswɛɛŋ anà ndɛɛl yi kikɔb a Mwol Yɛsu Klistɔ: wɛy ba bàsäl unsà duu anà badi isaa a mpay aba ŋakwo.
\v 13 Akà bɛ, atɔŋ, twon làn'yɔn mukyer ubwaŋ.
\v 14 Isàkal naa mbuur uläb anki nswɛɛŋ kan'pà bi uboo a un'kaan wà, lun'syebà ubwaŋàbwaŋ, twon lan'kal un'tüüb anà nde, ntɔn nde umɛn nswɛn.
\v 15 Wɛɛ, twon lun'wɛl asànaa un'yiiŋ, lun'weey asànaa un'tɔŋ.
\s1 Nsaak anà mbɔr
\p 
\v 16 Wɛy Mwol a duu, kàlapɛ duu nde ŋakwo taaŋ lanswà anà u mbwo yanswà. Wɛy Mwol ukäl anà bɛ banswà.
\p 
\v 17 Mbɔr yi yan'kɔɔ amɛ ŋakwo Pɔl. Mɛ in'fàsà kɔɔ unsà un'kaan umwɛy umwɛy in'fàsɔn mɛ.
\p 
\v 18 Wɛy kab a ngway a Mwol abi Yɛsu Klistɔ làkäl anà bɛ banswà.
